Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:05.10,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,By January 1986, the\Nspace shuttle had
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:07.16,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,flown 24 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:09.88,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Each flight reinforced\None idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:11.36,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The system worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:14.04,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Across those flights,\Nengineers documented
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:15.71,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,O-ring damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:18.71,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Erosion, blow-by, hot\Ngas pass seals
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:20.92,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,designed to hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:24.45,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Low-temperature\Nflights all showed distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:26.25,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,But each flight\Nsurvived, and the warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:28.07,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,lost force.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:30.74,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Danger became a known\Ncondition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:33.38,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,A stop signal became a\Nline item.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:36.19,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The night before\NChallenger, engineers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:37.95,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,recommended against\Nlaunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:39.98,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The burden shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:41.83,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Instead of proving it\Nsafe to fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:43.63,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,they were asked to\Nprove it was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:45.42,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,unsafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:48.31,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,On the coldest morning\Nthe program had
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.20,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,ever faced, 73 seconds\Nwas all the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:52.09,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,physics needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.35,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The warning was never\Nmissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:56.23,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It had been made\Nsurvivable for too
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:57.16,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:00.53,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Small causes, massive\Nconsequences.
